• Authentication
    • Account Setting
      • put Update an account settings
    • Company
      • post Create new company admin by supply chain
      • get Get company admin list by supply chain
      • get Find supply company admin by ID
      • put Update an existing supply user by ID
      • delete Delete supply company admin by ID
    • Member
      • post Add new member by company admin
      • get Get company member list by company admin
      • get Find Company Member by ID
      • put Update an existing company member
      • delete Delete Company Member
    • Product By Admin
      • post Add a new product to the supply chain
      • get Get All Products
      • get Find product by ID
      • put Update an existing product
      • delete Deletes a product
    • Product By Company
      • post Add a new product to the supply chain by company admin
      • get Get Products Listing Based On Company Admin
      • get Find Product Related to company and based on id
      • put Update an existing product by company admin
      • delete Deletes Company Admin Product
    • Workflow
      • post Add a new workflow by supply chain
      • get Get All Workflow by supply chain
      • get Find workflow by ID
      • put Update an existing workflow
      • delete Deletes a Workflow
      • put Change workflow mode an existing workflow
    • Workflow Step
      • post Add a new workflow step to the supply chain
      • get Find All Steps using particular Workflow id
      • get Find workflow step by assigned member step ID
      • put Update an existing workflow step
    • Workflow Company
      • get Get Workflow Listing Based On Company Admin
    • Workflow Member
      • get Find first step members by workflow ID
    • Start Workflow
      • post Start workflow and send mail to the supply chain
    • Activity
      • post Add a new activity to the supply chain
      • get Get All Activity
      • get Find activity by ID
      • post Correct the previous posted activity to the supply chain
      • post Add a new activity to the supply chain
      • get Get All Activity
      • get Find activity by ID
      • post Correct the previous posted activity to the supply chain
      • get Find previous company member posted activity product batches by ID
      • get Find report by outBatch
      • get Find report by outBatch
      • get Find batch track and trace report by outBatch
    • Assign Member By Company
      • put Assigned/Reassigned/Blocked member for workflow activity.
      • put Resend notification to member for workflow activity.
      • get Get all assigned member for workflow particular activity.
    • Upload
      • post Upload a file - .jpeg, png, gif , doc, csv , xls, pdf

    Powered by Docsiya

    VOTTUN API (2.0.0)

    Vottun protocol provides API for developer to integrate in their application like Android / IOS / Web Application

    swagger 2 Source url

    Authentication

    API key

    An API key is a special token (x-api-key) that you need to provide in header when making API calls, Like: { x-api-key: "TOKEN_VALUE" }

    Account Setting

    Update an account settings

    Update an workflow settings

    put https://api.vottun.com/api/v2 /supply/account/settings/
    • Request
    • Response
    • Coding

    body

    body required
    Supply account settings
    • Example Value
    • Model
    {
    "allow_nested_workflow": ""
}
    • allow_nested_workflow Boolean Description: Enable and Disable nested workflow settings

    Successfully Updated

    "message": ""

  --body '{"allow_nested_workflow":""}'

          import requests

}

          Company

          Create new company admin by supply chain

          Add new company admin by supply chain

          post https://api.vottun.com/api/v2 /supply/company/
          • Request
          • Response
          • Coding

          body

          body required
          Create new user by supply chain admin, - Company Admin
          • Example Value
          • Model
          {
    "supply_chain_email": "",
    "first_name": "",
    "last_name": "",
    "email": "",
    "phone": "",
    "organization": "",

    "account_settings": "",
    "view_product": "",

    "workflow_menu_pre": "",
    "download_activities_pre": ""
}
          • supply_chain_email String Description: Supply chain email address
          • first_name String Description: User first name
          • last_name String Description: User last name
          • email String Description: User email address
          • phone String Description: User phone number
          • organization String Description: Company Name
          • university_avatar String Description: User profile avatar
          • account_settings Boolean Description: User can able to access account settings menu
          • view_product Boolean Description: User can able to access view product menu
          • view_activity Boolean Description: User can able to access view activity menu
          • add_product Boolean Description: User can able to access add product
          • change_password Boolean Description: User can able to access change password menu
          • admin_prv Boolean Description: User is admin
          • dashboard_prv Boolean Description: User can able to access dashboard menu
          • producttrack_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access product batch track
          • producttrace_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access product trace menu
          • productloc_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access product location menu
          • member_menu_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access member menu
          • workflow_menu_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access workflow menu
          • download_activities_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access download activities

              • Request
              • Response
              • Coding

              query

              supply_chain_email required
              string
              Supply chain admin email address
              page optional
              integer
              Next page number
              name optional
              string
              Search company admin by name
              email optional
              string
              Search company admin by email address

              200

              List all company admin of supply chain admin
              • Example Value
              • Model

        "university_avatar": "",
        "organization": "",
        "is_active": "",
        "is_deleted": ""
    }]
}

              • next String Description: Next Page URL

              • results Array

                                        Member

                                        Add new team member by company admin

                                        Add new team member by company admin

                                        post https://api.vottun.com/api/v2 /supply/company/member/
                                        • Request
                                        • Response
                                        • Coding

                                        body

                                        body required
                                        Create new member for company admin to the supply chain
                                        • Example Value
                                        • Model
                                        {
    "company_admin_email": "",
    "first_name": "",
    "last_name": "",
    "email": "",
    "phone": "",
    "organization": "",
    "university_avatar": "",
    "certificate": "",
    "issue_certificate": "",
    "account_settings": "",
    "change_password": "",
    "producttrack_pre": "",
    "producttrace_pre": "",
    "productloc_pre": ""
}
                                        • company_admin_email String Description: Company admin email address
                                        • first_name String Description: Member first name
                                        • last_name String Description: Member last name
                                        • email String Description: Member email address
                                        • phone String Description: Member phone number
                                        • organization String Description: Company Name
                                        • university_avatar String Description: Member profile avatar
                                        • certificate Boolean Description: Member can able to see certificate (i.e. See posted activities)
                                        • issue_certificate Boolean Description: Member can able to issue certificate (i.e. allow to post activities)
                                        • account_settings Boolean Description: Member can able to access account settings menu
                                        • change_password Boolean Description: Member can able to access change password menu
                                        • producttrack_pre Boolean Description: User can able to access product batch track
                                        • producttrace_pre Boolean Description: Member can able to access product trace menu
                                        • productloc_pre Boolean Description: Member can able to access product location menu

                                        201

                                        Successfully Created
                                        • Example Value

                                                                                                                                                              Workflow Step

                                                                                                                                                              Add a new workflow step to the supply chain

                                                                                                                                                              post https://api.vottun.com/api/v2 /supply/steps/workflow/
                                                                                                                                                              • Request
                                                                                                                                                              • Response

    "current_emails": "",
    "workflow_id": "",
    "role": "",
    "is_qc": "",
    "step": "",
    "field_set": [{
        "type": "",
        "required": "",
        "save": "",
        "show": "",
        "is_lock_it": "",
        "out_box": "",
        "in_box": "",

        ],

            "user": "",
            "company_name": "",
            "email": ""
        }]
    }],
    "no_out_badge": 0,
    "show_role": "",
    "is_final_step": "",
    "graphic_show_role": ""
}
                                                                                                                                                              • current_emails String Description: Multiple Email of the Company Admin
                                                                                                                                                              • workflow_id String Description: Id of the workflow
                                                                                                                                                              • role String Description: Role of the user
                                                                                                                                                              • is_qc Boolean Description: Assigned user is quality check user
                                                                                                                                                              • step Integer Description: Step Number of the user
                                                                                                                                                              • field_set Array
                                                                                                                                                                • type String Description: Field type
                                                                                                                                                                • required Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • save Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • show Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • is_lock_it Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • out_box Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • in_box Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • primary Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • enable_furture Integer Enum: Description: type of datepicker, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - Any Date, 2 - Past Date, 3 - Current Date, 4 - Future Date
                                                                                                                                                                • dateformat Integer Enum: Description: type of format, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - mm/dd/yyyy, 2 - dd/mm/yyyy
                                                                                                                                                                • automatic Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • label String Description: Hint about the field
                                                                                                                                                                • name String Description: Name of the field
                                                                                                                                                                • placeholder String Description: Name of the field
                                                                                                                                                                • is_map_it Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • is_description Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                • value Array Description: User Input value. (Note: If Company Product OR Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown then have to pass field value as in array (list) format. i.e : ['','','']. if final step Product (choose single) then have to pass value as in array format single value. ie. : ['key-1']. If others field type then value should be in array format single string. i.e: ['string']. If field type is 'timestamp' then value should be ['dd-mm-yyyy HH:MM AM/PM'] or if field type is 'date' then value should be ['yyyy-mm-dd'])
                                                                                                                                                                • options Array
                                                                                                                                                                  • label String Description: Name of the option
                                                                                                                                                                  • key String Description: Value of the option
                                                                                                                                                                  • step Integer Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step number.
                                                                                                                                                                  • role String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's role.
                                                                                                                                                                  • user String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's first name & last name and organization name.
                                                                                                                                                                  • company_name String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown and also the user act as member. It have the value of next step member's company admin first name & last name.
                                                                                                                                                                  • email String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's email.
                                                                                                                                                              • no_out_badge Integer Description: Total out batch to generate
                                                                                                                                                              • show_role Boolean Description: Display this step in the Activity Header
                                                                                                                                                              • is_final_step Boolean Description: Generate the end user report QR code in this step.
                                                                                                                                                              • graphic_show_role Boolean Description: Display this step in the traceability graphical chart

                                                                                                                                                              Successfully Created

                                                                                                                                                                          • issuer_email String Description: Current step issuer user email
                                                                                                                                                                          • assigned_members ArrayDescription: Multiple members assigned for same step - Member email id (string)
                                                                                                                                                                            • assigned_companies ArrayDescription: Multiple company admins assigned for same step - company email id (string)
                                                                                                                                                                              • step_id String Description: Current step id
                                                                                                                                                                              • workflow_id String Description: Id of the workflow
                                                                                                                                                                              • role String Description: Role of the user
                                                                                                                                                                              • step Integer Description: Step Number of the user
                                                                                                                                                                              • field_set Array
                                                                                                                                                                                • type String Description: Field type
                                                                                                                                                                                • required Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • save Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • show Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • is_lock_it Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • out_box Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • in_box Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • primary Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • enable_furture Integer Enum: Description: type of datepicker, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - Any Date, 2 - Past Date, 3 - Current Date, 4 - Future Date
                                                                                                                                                                                • dateformat Integer Enum: Description: type of format, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - mm/dd/yyyy, 2 - dd/mm/yyyy
                                                                                                                                                                                • automatic Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • label String Description: Hint about the field
                                                                                                                                                                                • name String Description: Name of the field
                                                                                                                                                                                • placeholder String Description: Name of the field
                                                                                                                                                                                • is_map_it Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • is_description Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                • value Array Description: User Input value. (Note: If Company Product OR Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown then have to pass field value as in array (list) format. i.e : ['','','']. if final step Product (choose single) then have to pass value as in array format single value. ie. : ['key-1']. If others field type then value should be in array format single string. i.e: ['string']. If field type is 'timestamp' then value should be ['dd-mm-yyyy HH:MM AM/PM'] or if field type is 'date' then value should be ['yyyy-mm-dd'])
                                                                                                                                                                                • options Array
                                                                                                                                                                                  • label String Description: Name of the option
                                                                                                                                                                                  • key String Description: Value of the option
                                                                                                                                                                                  • step Integer Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step number.
                                                                                                                                                                                  • role String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's role.
                                                                                                                                                                                  • user String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's first name & last name and organization name.
                                                                                                                                                                                  • company_name String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown and also the user act as member. It have the value of next step member's company admin first name & last name.
                                                                                                                                                                                  • email String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's email.
                                                                                                                                                                              • no_out_badge Integer Description: Total out batch to generate
                                                                                                                                                                              • show_role Boolean Description: Display this step in the Activity Header
                                                                                                                                                                              • is_final_step Boolean Description: Generate the end user report QR code in this step.
                                                                                                                                                                              • graphic_show_role Boolean Description: Display this step in the traceability graphical chart
                                                                                                                                                                              • is_blocked Boolean Description: User is blocked by admin
                                                                                                                                                                              • is_qc Boolean Description: User role is quality check
                                                                                                                                                                              • unique_code String Description: unique code which is previous step company member posted
                                                                                                                                                                              • in_batch_id String Description: out batch id of previous step company member posted
                                                                                                                                                                              • out_batch_id String Description: Out batch ID
                                                                                                                                                                              • primary_key String Description: If primary field is true then it should same key name
                                                                                                                                                                                • primary_value String Description: If primary field is true then it should same value
                                                                                                                                                                                  • created String Description: Created Date of the workflow step (System Generate)
                                                                                                                                                                                  • modified String Description: Modified Date of the workflow step (System Generate)

                                                                                                                                                                                  400

                                                                                                                                                                                  Invalid ID supplied
                                                                                                                                                                                  • Example Value
                                                                                                                                                                                  • Model

If others field type then value should be in array format single string. i.e: ['string']. If field type is 'timestamp' then value should be ['dd-mm-yyyy HH:MM AM/PM'] or if field type is 'date' then value should be ['yyyy-mm-dd'])
                                                                                                                                                                                                      • options Array
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • label String Description: Name of the option
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • key String Description: Value of the option
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • step Integer Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step number.
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • role String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's role.
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • user String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's first name & last name and organization name.
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • company_name String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown and also the user act as member. It have the value of next step member's company admin first name & last name.
                                                                                                                                                                                                        • email String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's email.
                                                                                                                                                                                                    • no_out_badge Integer Description: Total out batch to generate
                                                                                                                                                                                                    • show_role Boolean Description: Display this step in the Activity Header
                                                                                                                                                                                                    • is_final_step Boolean Description: Generate the end user report QR code in this step.
                                                                                                                                                                                                    • graphic_show_role Boolean Description: Display this step in the traceability graphical chart

                                                                                                                                                                                                    200

                                                                                                                                                                                                          • dateformat Integer Enum: Description: type of format, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - mm/dd/yyyy, 2 - dd/mm/yyyy

If others field type then value should be in array format single string. i.e: ['string'].                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     • product String Description: Only for final step product id pass as string. i.e : 'product-key-1'. For other steps it should empty value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • issuer_email String Description: Email of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • workflow_id String Description: Workflow ID
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • unique_code String Description: QR code value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • in_batch_id String Description: In batch ID
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • out_batch_id String Description: Out batch ID
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • is_qc Boolean Description: step is Quality Check user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • field_set Array
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • value Array Description: User Input value. (Note: If Company Product OR Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown then have to pass field value as in array (list) format. i.e : ['','','']. if final step Product (choose single) then have to pass value as in array format single value. ie. : ['key-1']. If others field type then value should be in array format single string. i.e: ['string']. If field type is 'timestamp' then value should be ['dd-mm-yyyy HH:MM AM/PM'] or if field type is 'date' then value should be ['yyyy-mm-dd'])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • options Array
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • label String Description: User selected value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • key String Description: User selected value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • step Integer Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step number.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • role String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's role.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • user String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's first name & last name and organization name.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • company_name String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown and also the user act as member. It have the value of next step member's company admin first name & last name.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • email String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's email.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • name String Description: Field name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • label String Description: Field name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • type String Description: Field type
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • placeholder String Description: Hint about the fields
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • is_lock_it Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • save Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • automatic Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • show Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • out_box Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • in_box Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • is_map_it Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • is_description Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • primary Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • enable_furture Integer Enum: Description: type of datepicker, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - Any Date, 2 - Past Date, 3 - Current Date, 4 - Future Date
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • dateformat Integer Enum: Description: type of format, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - mm/dd/yyyy, 2 - dd/mm/yyyy
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • required Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • primary_key String Description: If primary field is true then it should same key name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • primary_value String Description: If primary field is true then it should same value

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • enable_furture Integer Enum: Description: type of datepicker, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - Any Date, 2 - Past Date, 3 - Current Date, 4 - Future Date
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • dateformat Integer Enum: Description: type of format, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - mm/dd/yyyy, 2 - dd/mm/yyyy

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • user Object
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • id String Description: Id of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • first_name String Description: First name of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • last_name String Description: Last name of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • email String Description: Email ID of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • phone String Description: Phone number of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • profile_pic String Description: Profile Picture of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • organization String Description: Organization name of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • company_pic String Description: Company profile picture of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • is_active Boolean Description: status of the user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • created String Description: Created Date of the user (System Generate)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • modified String Description: Modified Date of the user (System Generate)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • product Object
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • id String Description: ID of the product
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • barcode String Description: Barcode of the product
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • sup_barcode String Description: Optional/Second Barcode of the product
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • title String Description: Name of the product
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • image String Description: Image URL of the product
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • description String Description: Product description with HTML tags
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • barcodeimage String Description: Fixed product QR code
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • enduser_qr_type Integer Enum: Description: 1 - Dynamic, 2 - Fixed
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • created String Description: Created Date of the product (System Generate)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • modified String Description: Modified Date of the product (System Generate)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • in_batch_id String Description: In batch ID
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • out_batch_id String Description: Out batch ID
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • evidence String Description: Evidence link of the blockchain
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • blockchain Integer Description: 1 - Ethereum, 2 - Hyperledger, 3 - Alastria
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • transaction_address String Description: Transaction Address of the blockchain
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • field_set Array
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • value Array Description: User Input value. (Note: If Company Product OR Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown then have to pass field value as in array (list) format. i.e : ['','','']. if final step Product (choose single) then have to pass value as in array format single value. ie. : ['key-1']. If others field type then value should be in array format single string. i.e: ['string']. If field type is 'timestamp' then value should be ['dd-mm-yyyy HH:MM AM/PM'] or if field type is 'date' then value should be ['yyyy-mm-dd'])
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • options Array
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • label String Description: User selected value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • key String Description: User selected value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • step Integer Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step number.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • role String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's role.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • user String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's first name & last name and organization name.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • company_name String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown and also the user act as member. It have the value of next step member's company admin first name & last name.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • email String Description: This field will appear only if the field type is Next Step User OR Quality Check User dropdown. It have the value of next step member's email.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • name String Description: Field name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • label String Description: Field name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • type String Description: Field type
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • placeholder String Description: Hint about the fields
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • is_lock_it Boolean Description: required / optional

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • show Boolean Description: required / optional

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • in_box Boolean Description: required / optional

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • enable_furture Integer Enum: Description: type of datepicker, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - Any Date, 2 - Past Date, 3 - Current Date, 4 - Future Date
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • dateformat Integer Enum: Description: type of format, here 0 it means if field is not 'date' or 'datetime' then only it should be 0 otherwise have to pass mentioned value only, i.e: 0 - false, 1 - mm/dd/yyyy, 2 - dd/mm/yyyy
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • required Boolean Description: required / optional
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • locations Array

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • lng Number Description: Longitude value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • qrcode String Description: QrCode URL of the posted activity
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • unique_codes String Description: unique code of the posted activity
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • no_out_badge Integer Description: Number of out badge
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • show_role Boolean Description: Show role

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • primary_key String Description: If primary field is true then it should same key name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • primary_value String Description: If primary field is true then it should same value
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • created String Description: Created Date of the product (System Generate)
